title: Clashes in Pakistan as police try to arrest former Prime Minister Imran Khan
description: Supporters of Pakistan's former Prime Minister Imran Khan clashed with police seeking to arrest him outside his home on Tuesday, even as the longtime politician told CNN that he was "mentally prepared to spend the night in a cell."

title: Tilda Swinton says she will not be wearing a mask on set of new movie
description: Three years into the pandemic, Tilda Swinton is ready to put Covid-19-related film set rules behind her.

title: Ireland women's rugby team switch to dark shorts amid period anxieties
description: The Ireland women's rugby team has made a permanent switch from white to navy shorts in response to players' concerns about period anxieties.
